---
import "../styles/style.css";
---

<head>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400..900&family=Roboto+Condensed:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&family=Roboto:ital,wght@0,100;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,700;0,900;1,100;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,700;1,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400..900&family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&family=Roboto+Condensed:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&family=Roboto:ital,wght@0,100;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,700;0,900;1,100;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,700;1,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>

<section class="livesalg">
  <h1>LIVE SALG</h1>

  <p>Følg med på vores Facebook hvor vi holder livesalg HVER onsdag kl. 14</p>

  <a href="#">
    <img src="../img/facebook_grey.svg" alt="facebook" />
    Sæt en påmindelse her
  </a>

  <style>
    .livesalg {
      background-color: #f9f2f2;
      padding: 1.5rem 6rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      row-gap: 1rem;
      border-top: 0.5px solid #3c3636;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid #3c3636;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .livesalg h1,
    .livesalg p,
    .livesalg a {
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 40px;
      /* text-align: center; */
      font-family: orbitron;
      color: #1b72d0;
    }

    .livesalg p {
      font-family: poppins;
    }

    .livesalg a {
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-family: poppins;
      color: #3c3636;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 12px;
    }

    .livesalg a:hover {
      color: #1b72d0;
    }
    .livesalg a img {
      display: block;
      margin: auto;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    @media (min-width: 700px) {
      .livesalg {
        /* background-color: #f9f2f2; */
        padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem;
        /* display: flex; */
        flex-direction: unset;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        column-gap: 2rem;
        row-gap: unset;
        /* border-top: 0.5px solid #3c3636; */
        /* border-bottom: 0.5px solid #3c3636; */
        /* margin-bottom: 2rem; */
      }

      .livesalg h1 {
        text-align: left;
        text-wrap: nowrap;
      }
      .livesalg p {
        text-align: left;
      }
      .livesalg a {
        text-align: center;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-family: poppins;
        color: #3c3636;
        font-size: 12px;
        line-height: 12px;
      }
      .livesalg a img {
        display: block;
        margin: auto;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</section>
